This is Perl module Mojo::Server::Reversehttp.

INSTALLATION

Mojo::Server::Reversehttp installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan Mojo::Server::Reversehttp

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Mojo::Server::Reversehttp documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Mojo::Server::Reversehttp

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

